        {
            "title": "美國指控四人向中國走私英偉達先進晶片",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國指控四人向中國走私英偉達先進晶片\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tBWyVTHxsVSWCUXBSiy7bw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-07/cc759a70-3a87-11ef-becd-1729fd44ed4a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國指控四人向中國走私英偉達先進晶片</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
